de.take_weiland.mods.commons.config

Annotation Type Item


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Item
    Mark that this Field, also annotated with @GetProperty, represents an Item ID
    The effect of this is that Configuration.getItem will be used instead
    Also makes the category of this Property default to Configuration.CATEGORY_ITEM rather than Configuration.CATEGORY_GENERAL
    Author:
    diesieben07
